Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹竿喔，要买竹竿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹竿喔，要买竹竿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不要的东西吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说过这里的夏天很热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季才刚过\N热成这样太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想装台冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，没有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是生病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点中暑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中暑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指天气太热而没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能老是这么懒散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正补习班也有冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是早点去读书好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，招待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全馆空调系统检测通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说在下一节课前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷气就会修好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在出个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人答得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会我请大家吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要草莓牛奶冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，要答得出来才有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答题的学生要由我来选
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就来回答看看\N课本第25页的第3题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最基础的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举例说明好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经常用到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么热啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为冷气坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄坏的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干我什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看起来很郁卒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你今天有没有空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在打工前有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一节英文课的笔记\N能不能借我抄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我请你吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的字也未免太潦草了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个像颠倒音符的是什么字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是 U 啦， U
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也叫 U 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正内容是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将英语课本\N第158页第六行开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻译成英文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we shouid piaced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among the causes\Nof happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or among the causes\Nof unhappiness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may perhaps be regarded\Nas a dreadfui question
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错\NThere is certainiy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了，丝茉茉\NThere is certainiy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你这里抄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉头脑真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉装有英日翻译软件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还能帮你出题目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛮方便的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想借丝茉茉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是报答你借我笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借你一天没关系喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠电脑好像不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笔记晚点再还我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜，谢谢请客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师在上课时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有提到\N明天可能会有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理员小姐给的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得闻到这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让人有夏天的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫作夏天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对，不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说季节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气热是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气冷是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气温暖是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚会是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过份，竟然把人家给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不是忘了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该说是夏天的错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是一场夏日的回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对没有玩弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的，认真的，诚心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓到你了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住一晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是本须和的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有男生房间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么自己跑进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎，别在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀\Nちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妳叫ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是孺子可教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:08:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝给他醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师你才刚喝过不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要住一晚是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么行不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么做比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想办法熬到天亮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样更不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是愿意让我住一晚罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想对我做什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师你打算喝这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，很平常，很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树教过我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个形状怎么形容？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在笑的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是好想当喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小学老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你原本想当小学老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，原本是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我老公说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小学要是当了班导师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会忙到没时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以反对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被老公反对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你结婚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得电脑比较可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人类比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟电脑在一起比较快乐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以请你下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该停了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“国王游戏”很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我被命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你签运那么差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像个男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽签的时候干脆点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ也抽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国王是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该做点刺激的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺激？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到二号的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻国王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么请拿到二号的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是几号？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又好像有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来玩亲亲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国王的命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神已经不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要亲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是本须和的电脑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托不要吓我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有精神起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对没有想歪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是想其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砰一声倒下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来我睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會吵醒ちぃ的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原来是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过好真实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经天亮了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只穿内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在梦里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…\N早安，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，脸湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你那个穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没欺负你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺负…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟第一次要给喜欢的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和你还是很纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是天气热脱下衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟本须和都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全部看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算一般尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树是一般的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，這個不必記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我盥洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为一开始就打算来借住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就打算在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…为什么你要来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为胆小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经出门了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得这位上礼拜在海边见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，敝姓清水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，补习班的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天功课一定进步不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直叹气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能被她误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在在意那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是真误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下次去帮你解释
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这确实让人伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被误会跟我在交往的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是老师比较伤脑筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师在烦恼些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以找我谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟我听到的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个跟现在说的无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真累人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出门了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好严重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很困的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天清水老师突然来我房间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始点名…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师，点名就不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，翻开第26页…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是惨毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保一副可怕的表情\N一句话也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我为他操心\N打工时老出错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还要被雨淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早点睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸口为什么湿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子真是一点也不老实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不老实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸上的妆都糊掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的女人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子最可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许会被人看见喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在补习班教书的是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在补习班读书的是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师是补习班老师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师\N跟补习班学生抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个补习班学生是新保
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师是有夫之妇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，什麼都不做」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来也只能这样

